  ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ -----
  $$\log\eta_{\text{app}} = a + \frac{b}{\ln\text{AS}} + \frac{c}{\text{AS}^{1.5}}{\mathit{Φ}} + \text{d} \cdot \exp\left( {- \text{AS}} \right) + e \cdot {\mathit{Φ}} \cdot \ln{\mathit{Φ}},$$   (5)
